title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 19 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 19 2022
description:
Jaw-dropping: Stacey Abrams says abortion is the cure for inflation. Buck says, "They usually don't say things like this out loud: 'Milk is pricey. So go abort some children. That'll help you.'" Pelosi says Biden's first two years have been better than any president in generations. Clay says, "Nancy Pelosi is doing a default praising of herself since she is partnered with Joe Biden." Dr. Oz pulls ahead in overseas betting markets for first time. Kari Lake's opponent is afraid to debate her. Buck triggered by Meghan Markle's objectification complaints.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
